credit_line: Gift of Mr. and Mrs. Abraham M. Adler
title: Psyche Rescued by a Fisherman
description: Set of scenic wallpaper "Les Amours de Psyche", consisting of 26 panels which form 12 scenes based on the Jean de la Fontiane story  "Les Amours de Psyche" (1669). Scene depicts Psyche being rescued by a fisherman.
name: Scenic - paper
